query.sql:
select ViceNews_FullOISData.rowid,Date, NumberOfSubjects,
  Fatal.value as Fatal,
  SubjectArmed.value as SubjectArmed,
  SubjectRace.value as SubjectRace,
  SubjectGender.value as SubjectGender,
  Department.value as Department,
  city.value as city
from ViceNews_FullOISData
  join Fatal on ViceNews_FullOISData.Fatal = Fatal.id
  join SubjectArmed on ViceNews_FullOISData.SubjectArmed = SubjectArmed.id
  join SubjectRace on ViceNews_FullOISData.SubjectRace = SubjectRace.id
  join SubjectGender on ViceNews_FullOISData.SubjectGender = SubjectGender.id
  join Department on ViceNews_FullOISData.Department = Department.id
  join city on ViceNews_FullOISData.city = city.id
order by ViceNews_FullOISData.rowid limit 1000
